Enum Class CardState

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<CardState>
it.polimi.ingsw.is25am33.model.enumFiles.CardState
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<CardState>, Constable
public enum CardState extends Enum<CardState>
Represents the various states that a card can transition through during game play. Each state corresponds to a specific phase or action in the game's card resolution process. These states are used to control game flow and determine valid actions at different points in card execution.
